Total of 22 exercises in the categories of “eyes” and “ears” as well as 
combinations of both areas are waiting for the players. “THINK ® Train 
Your Senses”  let the player try first on his weaknesses and improve his 
skills through targeted training. Matches will be played on the basis of 
an analysis and an individual’s daily schedule.